sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Webhook as KServe Webhook<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Controller as KServe Controller<br/>Manager
    participant S3 as S3/GCS/Azure Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Knative as Knative Service
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Istio Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant Activator as Knative Activator<br/>8012/TCP HTTP
    participant Predictor as Model Predictor Pod<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Transformer as Model Transformer Pod<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Explainer as Model Explainer Pod<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,Controller: Flow 1: Model Deployment via InferenceService

    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl create InferenceService<br/>Auth: Client cert
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /mutate-serving-kserve-io-v1beta1-inferenceservice<br/>mTLS
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Mutated InferenceService
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-serving-kserve-io-v1beta1-inferenceservice<br/>mTLS
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation result
    K8sAPI-->>User: InferenceService created

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch InferenceService CRDs<br/>ServiceAccount token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Knative Service/Deployment<br/>ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Resources created

    Note over S3,Predictor: Storage Initializer downloads model
    Predictor->>S3: Download model artifacts<br/>AWS IAM/GCP SA/Azure Key
    S3-->>Predictor: Model files

    Note over Client,Explainer: Flow 2: Inference Request (Serverless Mode)

    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/models/model:predict<br/>Optional Bearer Token
    Gateway->>Activator: Forward request<br/>HTTP
    Activator->>Predictor: Inference request<br/>Optional Token

    alt With Transformer
        Predictor->>Transformer: Pre-process request<br/>HTTP/8080
        Transformer-->>Predictor: Transformed input
    end

    Predictor->>Predictor: Run inference
    Predictor-->>Activator: Prediction result

    alt With Explainer
        Activator->>Explainer: Explain request<br/>Optional Token
        Explainer-->>Activator: Explanation result
    end

    Activator-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON response

    Note over Client,Predictor: Flow 3: InferenceGraph Multi-Step Pipeline

    Client->>Gateway: POST to InferenceGraph endpoint<br/>Optional Bearer Token
    Gateway->>Predictor: Route to Router Pod<br/>HTTP/8080
    Predictor->>Predictor: Graph Node 1 (Model A)
    Predictor->>Predictor: Graph Node 2 (Model B)
    Predictor->>Predictor: Graph Node 3 (Ensemble)
    Predictor-->>Gateway: Pipeline result
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON response
